    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/7d2934f42cea253b34682f2bd5e32f9f.poster.avif?t=1729519301\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/7d2934f42cea253b34682f2bd5e32f9f.webm?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/7d2934f42cea253b34682f2bd5e32f9f.mp4?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >诸神的黄昏已然来临……</h2>在众神与巨人的冲突后被摧毁的旧世界废墟上，Gimle诞生了——人类重生的地方。新世界在预言中没有战争、饥饿和苦难。千百年来，不知为何它一直在与邪恶势力作斗争。与此同时，另一个令人不安的威胁正在到来——死亡将只是堕落者痛苦的开始。挪威战士布兰德作为人类最后的希望出现了——他会站起来战斗并揭开一个未实现的预言的秘密吗?<br><br>《Gimle》是一款受经典题材启发的等视角RPG游戏，拥有炫酷的像素图像。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/06c75be196919dc8c6ab594499e09a5d.poster.avif?t=1729519301\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/06c75be196919dc8c6ab594499e09a5d.webm?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/06c75be196919dc8c6ab594499e09a5d.mp4?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开始你的旅程吧！</h2>根据挪威神话探索Gimle的黑暗世界。探索森林灌丛和山路，探索邪恶的城镇和村庄，还有充满危险地下隧道的神秘坟墓。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/f5aadf50071d6a28ae930b4d1f4d23f1.poster.avif?t=1729519301\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/f5aadf50071d6a28ae930b4d1f4d23f1.webm?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/f5aadf50071d6a28ae930b4d1f4d23f1.mp4?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打败你的敌人！</h2>使用各种各样的武器-剑、矛、斧头、弓等等，掌握动态战斗系统并面对充满威胁的新世界！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/5507ded11a58359b79b6fbcc15ec7e6b.poster.avif?t=1729519301\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/5507ded11a58359b79b6fbcc15ec7e6b.webm?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/5507ded11a58359b79b6fbcc15ec7e6b.mp4?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驯服强大的力量！</h2>学习比普通魔法更强大的独特能力。使用你强大的天赋，发掘未实现的预言的奥秘。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/c40f031da117c38a2c06bba5af9054c6.poster.avif?t=1729519301\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/c40f031da117c38a2c06bba5af9054c6.webm?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/c40f031da117c38a2c06bba5af9054c6.mp4?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集独特的物品！</h2>利用收集资源和交易的可能，收集强大的物品和上古神器，这些物品最终将在你通过黑暗之地时大有帮助。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/3604c32759b7770b9b5a94e4a80d292a.poster.avif?t=1729519301\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/3604c32759b7770b9b5a94e4a80d292a.webm?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/3604c32759b7770b9b5a94e4a80d292a.mp4?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提升你的技能！</h2>成为维京世界的传奇！通过各种统计、科学和属性系统精通各种领域。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/9b8a949bfaec990fa536351df9923bcf.poster.avif?t=1729519301\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/9b8a949bfaec990fa536351df9923bcf.webm?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765920/extras/9b8a949bfaec990fa536351df9923bcf.mp4?t=1729519301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >书写新世界的故事！</h2>体验一个充满困难、模糊选择的暴烈世界，并面对艰难的后果。",
